{"tid":1453422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［學術討論］機場運作最驚d乜？","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:21:04.000Z","uid":258602,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf1684f40053f01af06284d0ec05abf09c6709c","tid":1453422,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:11:08.000Z","msg":"一定係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無人機/航拍機</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國機場噩夢：小小無人機為何令航空交通大混亂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-46651290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-46651290&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=2b1c9ef8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-46651290&h=bd1952b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-46651290</a><br />\n<br />\n只是機場範圍內見到有無人機，就一定會停飛直到無人機消失為止<br />\n<br />\n所以記得<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好係機場附近玩無人機</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果玩玩吓無人機俾怪風吹咗去機場點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U56HkXz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU56HkXz.png&h=db5fbdf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我建議盡量<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">控制無人機沿客運大樓/HAECO飛入機場中央</span></strong><br />\n原因：<br />\n1.紅線位於兩條跑道中間，一般不會有飛機飛行，以免撞機<br />\n2.控制塔位於機場中央，讓ATC更易發現無人機以安全處理<br />\n如做不到亦應令無人機盡量遠離跑道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>航空安全，人人有責</strong></span>"},{"pid":"484ccb25489830f2eee176a949bbda971611775a","tid":1453422,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:12:24.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"84671f1377c5b788237301aec1e58248ca5e309d","tid":1453422,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"航空安全，人人有責"},{"pid":"4aee3aa5efd63c92acaa0584c5cb72f9ab207f45","tid":1453422,"uid":227788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"Msg from 民航處航空塔員工<br />\nif you wanna block us , needs to block the shuttle station and tung Chung pier<br />\n<br />\n之前8月5佢安排過快艇去東涌接同事1<br />\n<br />\n只要有少少唔安全 我哋大條道理唔返工<br />\n<br />\n另外你哋可以試圍民航處總部 可以直接癱瘓晒我哋雷達管制 會比控制塔影響大好多倍<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好破壞雷達 大霧山同mount parker 最重要 一斷我哋會睇唔到飛機做唔到嘢 山上面又無人守"},{"pid":"327101abaf5f9af0515f8b6c082cff3e72a6f62c","tid":1453422,"uid":192052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"一早都咁講 搞咩雷達站 吃力不討好 一架無人機全停 如果唔怕死就送㗎無人機入國航嘅引擎到"},{"pid":"d0177e4e84f6d93f267bcb7035f7858be4a000f8","tid":1453422,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:14:46.000Z","msg":"航空安全，人人有責"},{"pid":"46081a9589e4c6daf5d4801391c4b45613cc658a","tid":1453422,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"記得機場唔好玩無人機，風爭都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfaed17d8a2cc934c23f4a30eb4f761a0e7377d4","tid":1453422,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"on9 仔，機場早就有干擾器干擾無人機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔撚好同我講干擾干擾器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1035dba615bd0f300e4d2533a44cc6ab24c0062f","tid":1453422,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:18:12.000Z","msg":"上機前好去處：香港機場 T2 展望台 Skydeck <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.runhotel.hk/2015/01/hong-kong-t2-skydes-aviation-discovery-centre.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.runhotel.hk%2F2015%2F01%2Fhong-kong-t2-skydes-aviation-discovery-centre.html&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpKzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=88eb0887\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.runhotel.hk/2015/01/hong-kong-t2-skydes-aviation-discovery-centre.html</a>"},{"pid":"6aefc3a4aebf1058773d5b03103a95430ffa7ddc","tid":1453422,"uid":258602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:21:04.000Z","msg":"航空安全，人人有責"}]}